00:30:37,060 --> 00:30:39,180
 And Brother Lawrence was working

571
00:30:39,180 --> 00:30:41,780
 in the kitchen of the monastery.

572
00:30:43,220 --> 00:30:45,620
 And he wrote a little book, "In the Presence of God,"

