00:30:45,620 --> 00:30:47,380
 or "Practice the Presence of God."

574
00:30:47,380 --> 00:30:51,420
 Now, that little book, he shared his secret

575
00:30:51,420 --> 00:30:55,960
 of how to live in the presence of God every day,

576
00:30:55,960 --> 00:30:56,960
 no matter what I do.

577
00:30:56,960 --> 00:31:01,440
 And his secret is, when he was struggling

578
00:31:01,440 --> 00:31:02,820
 with his relationship with God,

579
00:31:02,820 --> 00:31:07,740
 he find himself sometimes distant from God himself.

580
00:31:07,740 --> 00:31:10,420
 So he figured out some way to keep himself

581
00:31:10,420 --> 00:31:11,960
 in the presence of God.

582
00:31:11,960 --> 00:31:14,020
 So this is what he did.

583
00:31:14,020 --> 00:31:16,700
 Every day he was in the kitchen doing dishes,

584
00:31:16,700 --> 00:31:18,260
 very mundane work.

585
00:31:18,260 --> 00:31:23,620
 But he find the secret is, whenever he has time,

586
00:31:23,620 --> 00:31:25,020
 he would do a little prayer.

587
00:31:25,020 --> 00:31:28,500
 And that little prayer is very simple.

588
00:31:28,500 --> 00:31:32,580
 It's like, "God, I wanna do this for your sake.

589
00:31:32,580 --> 00:31:36,540
 "And God, I wanna do it for your honor, and help me."

590
00:31:36,540 --> 00:31:39,940
 It's just that simple prayer.

591
00:31:39,940 --> 00:31:42,140
 So he start his work in the morning,

592
00:31:42,140 --> 00:31:46,680
 pray that prayer.

593
00:31:46,680 --> 00:31:49,240
 And then he find that it's helpful for him

594
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:52,160
 to be aware that he is doing everything

595
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:53,860
 and living in the presence of God.

596
00:31:53,860 --> 00:31:59,820
 And then he increase it by doing that prayer at noon,

597
00:31:59,820 --> 00:32:04,680
 and then in the afternoon.

598
00:32:04,680 --> 00:32:07,400
 And then pretty much it becomes his second nature,

599
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:11,260
 that whenever he does the dishes,

600
00:32:11,260 --> 00:32:13,700
 whenever he mopping the floor,

601
00:32:13,700 --> 00:32:16,700
 he will pray to God silently, quietly,

602
00:32:16,700 --> 00:32:18,660
 and pray that, "God, I wanna live in your presence.

603
00:32:18,660 --> 00:32:20,420
 "I wanna do this for your honor."

604
00:32:20,420 --> 00:32:24,860
 That book, that secret,

605
00:32:24,860 --> 00:32:28,160
 became one of the Christian classics.

606
00:32:28,160 --> 00:32:31,680
 Everyone finds it helpful.

607
00:32:33,620 --> 00:32:38,620
 Find rest in every single moment that you can in your day.

608
00:32:38,620 --> 00:32:40,820
 Even when you're driving,

609
00:32:40,820 --> 00:32:43,660
 even when you're doing your work,

610
00:32:43,660 --> 00:32:46,600
 pray that little prayer,

611
00:32:46,600 --> 00:32:49,840
 and pray that, "God, I wanna live in your presence.

612
00:32:49,840 --> 00:32:51,840
 "Help me to be faithful.

613
00:32:51,840 --> 00:32:53,760
 "Help me to love you more."

614
00:32:53,760 --> 00:32:56,000
 No matter what you do, changing diapers,

615
00:32:56,000 --> 00:33:01,040
 mopping the floor, doing some mundane work,

616
00:33:01,920 --> 00:33:03,780
 you can live in the presence of God.

617
00:33:03,780 --> 00:33:06,660
 So I wanna invite you to be more faithful,

618
00:33:06,660 --> 00:33:09,220
 to really enjoy this sacred time,

619
00:33:09,220 --> 00:33:13,980
 one day a week, first day of week.

